  m_text: 'About Psyche Against the Universe


    Created by: Timothy Burke

    Azaria
    Mehanovic

    Abdur-Rahman Igram

    Rijul Sudesh


    A digital version of
    the "Psyche Against the Universe" card game created by Nihah Shah as part of
    the Psyche Inspire Program.


    The game aims to meet the intent of the original
    and provides a digital means of learning about the Psyche Mission as well as
    having fun.


    Sponsored by: Cassie Bowman, Arizona State Univerity through
    a partnership with NASA. Capstone Project for

    Penn State University, SWENG
    480 and 481.'
