  m_text: 'Goal: The goal of the game is to guide the player through the solar system
    who is on its way to asteroid Psyche-16. However the journey is not as empty
    as space may seem. The player will encounter unusual scenerios, and the solution
    they provide may provide them the boost the need to succeed.



    Set-Up: The
    user (You) selects an avatar to be you on this journey. After which, determine
    which game mode you want to play. Select the number of CPU players whom you wish
    to be challenged against. At this time also select any quality of life features
    you may want to use. When ready to begin your journey, press Start.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
